title: TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM
position: 0,0
---
<<u_add_var "u_met_robofac_intercom" "dialogue" "intercom" "yes">>
<<if npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    NPC: {random_line("So, do you need something?", "Yes, mercenary?", "Mercenary.", "Mercenary.", "Don't you have a mission to do?", "Well?", "Say it.", "Get with it.", "Make it quick.", "Don't loiter.", "Don't do anything stupid.", "Ugh I hate intercom duty…  Wait is the speaker still on?", "Please don't bother us senselessly.", "[Silence]", "[Crackles On]", "[A red LED blinks on]", "[Unintelligible]", "What's up with the interference in this thing?", "Speak slowly and clearly.  Please.", "Say again?", "If/you speak to/understand… you/me. Yes?")}
<<else>>
    <<if u_has_var("u_met_robofac_intercom", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
        NPC: We haven't changed our mind.  Go away.
    <<else>>
        NPC: Hold there.  I don't care how you got access to this location, but you are coming no further.  Go away.
    <<endif>>
<<endif>>
-> I was sent here by the traders at the refugee center.  They told me to deliver this hard drive to you. <<if (not u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and u_has_mission("MISSION_FREE_MERCHANTS_HUB_DELIVERY_1")>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_FREE_MERCHANT_DELIVERY_1>>
-> The traders also mentioned you were looking for help. <<if (not u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<if trial_roll("LIE", 1)>>
        <<jump MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_INTRODUCTION>>
    <<else>>
        <<jump MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_INTRODUCTION>>
    <<endif>>
-> Wait!  What?? <<if (not u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_FREE_MERCHANTS_HUB_DELIVERY_1")) and (not u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1"))>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_PLEAD>>
-> You do realize that the front door is just open? <<if (not u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_FREE_MERCHANTS_HUB_DELIVERY_1")) and (not u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1"))>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_PLEAD>>
-> Lets trade. <<if npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<start_trade>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM>>
-> Know when you'll get another shipment? <<if npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_RESTOCK>>
-> It's the apocalypse out here!  Please let me in! <<if (not u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_FREE_MERCHANTS_HUB_DELIVERY_1")) and (not u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1"))>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_PLEAD>>
-> I was just looking for valuables, maybe I can trade with you instead? <<if (not u_has_var("completed_free_merchants_hub_delivery_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not u_has_mission("MISSION_FREE_MERCHANTS_HUB_DELIVERY_1")) and (not npc_has_var("npc_failed_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")) and (not npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes"))>>
    <<if trial_roll("PERSUADE", 1)>>
        <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_TRADE>>
    <<else>>
        <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_NO_TRADE>>
    <<endif>>
-> Any jobs you need done? <<if u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<jump TALK_MISSION_LIST>>
-> What the hell were you testing out there? <<if u_has_var("completed_robofac_intercom_1", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_PROTOTYPE_ASK>>
-> So, about that protective gear? <<if u_has_mission("MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_3") and (not npc_has_var("npc_bought_protective_gear", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes"))>>
    <<jump TALK_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_BUY_PROTECTIVE_GEAR>>
-> I gotta go. <<if npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<stop>>
-> Alright, I'm leaving. <<if not npc_has_var("npc_intercom_trade", "dialogue", "intercom", "yes")>>
    <<stop>>
