NPC: Given the current context, we are willing to sell you a set of our protective gear: gas mask, suit and gear, at a considerable discount.  We will sell it for two of our coins.

the intercom: Hmm wait, we might not have your size...
-> [ 2 HGC ] Deal! <<if u_has_items("RobofacCoin", 2)>>
    <<u_sell_item "RobofacCoin" 0 2>>
    <<u_buy_item "mask_gas" 0 1>>
