title: MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_INTRODUCTION
position: 0,240
---
NPC: There's nothing you could do for us, now leave before I'm forced to…
[You hear a short, muffled conversation from across the intercom]

the intercom: Well, it seems we do have some use for you.  It's a dangerous task, but if you complete it we will allow you limited trading access.
-> Tell me about it.
    <<jump MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_OFFER>>
-> I'm not risking myself for a deal that bad.
    <<stop>>
===

title: MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_OFFER
position: 320,240
---
NPC: One of our scientists recently left the lab to perform a field test on a prototype robot, but failed to return, and has not been heard of since.  Investigate the test and return with her and the prototype.  Failing that, return with the data recorder that was attached to our prototype.
-> I'll do it!
    <<add_mission "MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1">>
    <<jump MISSION_ROBOFAC_INTERCOM_1_ACCEPTED>>
-> Not interested.
    <<stop>>
===

